Generative AI Engineer Roadmap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Generative AI engineering focuses on building systems that can create content such as text, images, code, audio, and video. A Generative AI Engineer works with large language models (LLMs), diffusion models, prompt engineering, retrieval systems, and AI application development to build intelligent, production-ready AI products.\
This roadmap takes a beginner from programming fundamentals to building advanced generative AI applications used in real-world products.\
